   <NoteLine></NoteLine>
   <NoteLine>Logs with speech which might be really appreciated just to keep track of what is happening,</NoteLine>
   <NoteLine>or just for fun.</NoteLine>
   <NoteLine></NoteLine>
   <NoteLine>You can pass in a prefix to the object which is said before every message, eg:</NoteLine>
